HEADWORD: Healall
<hw>Heal"all`</hw> <pr>(-⟦add⟧l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>A common herb of the Mint family (<spn>Brunella vulgaris</spn>),
destitute of active properties, but anciently thought to be a
panacea.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Heald</ent>⟦br⟧
